1. iterm: https://iterm2colorschemes.com/ search Lab Fox
	* go into iTerm preferences and untick the indicators: Profiles > Terminal > Show mark indicators.
    * font: https://www.nerdfonts.com/font-downloads
        - check: JetBrainsMono
        - check install instruction at the end of the page
2. tmux:
    * https://github.com/wfxr/tmux-power ('moon')
    * https://github.com/catppuccin/tmux

    Install plugin for tmux:
    1. git clone git@github.com:tmux-plugins/tmux-sensible.git ~/.tmux/plugins/tmux-sensible
    2. tmux source-file ~/.tmux.conf

3. zsh: https://github.com/romkatv/powerlevel10k
